'''马来西亚自力社会协会'''，简称'''自力社'''或'''DAYA'''，是[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]的[[非政府组织|非政府组织]]，由[[蔡添强|蔡添强]]成立并且推介于2020年7月25日。同样来自[[人民公正党|公正党]]的颜贝倪与陈记光也是该社成员。此外，原住民社运分子{{tsl|en|Amani Williams Hunt Abdullah|巴东尼律师}}与[[净选盟|净选盟]]前主席[[安美嘉|安美嘉]]也加入该社。<ref name="东方日报">{{cite web |title=蔡添强非政府组织　自力社周六推介礼 |url=https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/index.php/news/nation/2020/07/23/353472 |website=马来西亚东方日报 |accessdate=2020-09-06}}</ref><ref name="Astro AWANI">{{cite web |author1=Faris Danial Razi |title=Tian Chua akui NGO Daya tiada kaitan dengan politik |url=https://www.astroawani.com/berita-politik/tian-chua-akui-ngo-daya-tiada-kaitan-dengan-politik-252778 |website=Astro AWANI |accessdate=2020-09-06 |archive-date=2020-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003035700/https://www.astroawani.com/berita-politik/tian-chua-akui-ngo-daya-tiada-kaitan-dengan-politik-252778 |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，推介礼当天亦有数名前公正党籍州议员的出席。<ref name="Malay Mail">{{cite web |author1=Radzi Razak |title=‘We are above politics, but not allergic to it’: PKR veep launches new NGO Daya to bring reform ideals back to Malaysia |url=https://www.malaymail.com/news/malaysia/2020/07/25/we-are-above-politics-but-not-allergic-to-it-pkr-veep-launches-new-ngo-daya/1888074 |website=Malay Mail |accessdate=2020-09-06 |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025072839/https://www.malaymail.com/news/malaysia/2020/07/25/we-are-above-politics-but-not-allergic-to-it-pkr-veep-launches-new-ngo-daya/1888074 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

蔡添强否认自力社是其个人的政治平台，该社的成立是为了透过技职训练，强化社群关系，以帮助弱势和贫困阶层。<ref name="透视大马">{{cite web |title=创立自立社没牵涉政治 蔡添强：我仍是公正党一份子 |url=https://www.themalaysianinsight.com/chinese/s/262931 |website=透视大马 |accessdate=2020-09-06}}</ref><ref name="团结面对疫情，重新整装出发">{{cite web |title=SERUAN UNTUK BERTINDAK: INISIATIF TERBARU SOLIDARITI |url=https://daya.my/seruan-untuk-bertindak-inisiatif-terbaru-solidariti/ |website=DAYA |accessdate=2021-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210904171856/https://daya.my/seruan-untuk-bertindak-inisiatif-terbaru-solidariti/ |archive-date=2021-09-05}}</ref>

